reviews.text: Nice place for lunch. Prices are reasonable for the food. Just a bit out of the way.....

How can sous vide go so wrong, this restaurant has totally missed the point of sous vide, the meat was tough and dry like it had been overcooked in an oven. 

The very point of sous vide is to hold the meat at the lowest possible cooking Temperature for a long time to cook the meat and remove any bacteria while keeping it as jucy and tender.

The best part of the meal was the sides, but even they were under seasoned and bland.

As another reviewer wrote, it's a Cantonese attempt at Western food, if you're into that then ok, each to their own, but for the price you'd be better to go somewhere else in my opinion.

Wonder where the good reviews come from, it’s so bad I wish I hadn’t been there for the pork and lamb. Pork was too lightly flavoured, not seared and came out plain. Lamb was dry and very hard to chew. Sides of asparagus was too old to chew for the bottom halves, while mushroom has super light flavours only. Would never go again.
Good service , good place and  good food.  We paid at the moment we order our food, I'm not complain I think is good way since they Only accept cash.

It's a typical Chinese Western place, relatively affordable and the quality of the food is not that good. If you want proper Western, better go elsewhere.

Also don't really like that their rating was based on people (friends or paid) to all rate their place 5 stars two weeks ago

reviews.text:
平時都鍾意周圍去, 影下相去發掘下D新餐廳,特別係小店! 今日就去左上環古董街同埋PMQ影相, 行到日落就係搵食既時間!朋友係上環返工同我介紹過呢間隱世餐廳, 位置唔算方便, 但識飲識食嘅朋友介紹到, 就突登行過黎食, 呢到門口有幾特別既老虎塗鴉, 只要認住呢個iconic 的塗鴉就一定識黎呢度!

飲品 - 檸檬薑茶$42
坐定定先叫左一壼清香怡人的檸檬薑茶,所有兩個人分享岩岩好

前菜 - 柚子菠菜沙律 $48
呢個沙律我同朋友都認為好好食，入面有柚子果粒,車厘茄, 紫椰菜, 沙律菜等,個汁好開胃, 沙律菠菜好新鮮, 好岩女仔食.

主菜 - 慢煮36小時紐西蘭牛面肉 $148 
慢煮幾時都係我最愛, 唔會有OVER COOK, 又唔會生得滯之餘又保留到肉汁。基本上控制到個適當溫度就唔會差得去邊!因為今日唔想食steak就揀左呢個牛面肉.牛面肉煮到好淋，再配個紅酒汁好好味.其實牛面肉真係第一次食，食落口感好似牛脷。個份量都唔小，兩個人女仔食係夠食有突。

SIDE DISH - 牛油炒蘆筍苗 $38
好香牛油味, 蘆筍苗食得出係新鮮貨, 無渣, 有菜蔬嘅鮮甜。加左少量調味,咸度剛好

第二主菜 - 肉醬意粉 $78
呢個意粉係特別為左個肉醬意粉怪朋友叫既, 佢一見到任何餐廳有肉醬意粉,就話都一定要叫。芝士份量好充,而且有拉絲!!芝士同肉醬份量夠哂多, 夠Mix  哂成個意粉, 肉醬好夠味, 岩哂我地呢對芝士控 +意粉控,好邪惡但係好好味

甜品 - 雜莓比利時窩夫配意大利雪糕 HKD$42
窩夫熱辣辣上枱, 最APPRECIATE 佢即叫即整, 唔會整好哂等係到。最鍾意比利時窩夫口感比普通果D窩夫實淨同埋煙韌, 外邊又脆脆地, 真係十個好味有一百個。 再配埋士多啤梨醬, 同配上士多啤梨和藍莓等的新鮮水果， 可以中和窩夫本身偏甜的味道。好FRESH!

叫左咁多野, 人均消費都唔洗$200! 仲要唔洗加一, 朋友真係無介紹錯!

慢煮都是這幾年才興起的，所以就決定入去試新野，這間餐廳的裝修很平易近人，屬於casual dining，坐下了一個比較靜的閣仔地方，看看餐牌, 選擇也蠻多。

慢煮36小時紐西蘭牛面肉10安士(Hk$148)

口感豐富，味道濃郁，醃法有紅酒燴牛尾的風味，慢煮確實將牛面肉煮得細嫩有肉汁，好味

法式油封鴨腿2支HK$98

這道菜其實是出名的法國菜餚之一，confit de canard, 製作十分之繁複，醃製也要數日，鴨腿外表金黃，由於可能慢煮的關係，食落鴨肉結實柔軟，再配合百里香Thyme，確有特別的風味，讚
Nice place for lunch. Prices are reasonable for the food. Just a bit out of the way.....

How can sous vide go so wrong, this restaurant has totally missed the point of sous vide, the meat was tough and dry like it had been overcooked in an oven. 

The very point of sous vide is to hold the meat at the lowest possible cooking Temperature for a long time to cook the meat and remove any bacteria while keeping it as jucy and tender.

The best part of the meal was the sides, but even they were under seasoned and bland.

As another reviewer wrote, it's a Cantonese attempt at Western food, if you're into that then ok, each to their own, but for the price you'd be better to go somewhere else in my opinion.

Wonder where the good reviews come from, it’s so bad I wish I hadn’t been there for the pork and lamb. Pork was too lightly flavoured, not seared and came out plain. Lamb was dry and very hard to chew. Sides of asparagus was too old to chew for the bottom halves, while mushroom has super light flavours only. Would never go again.
